flowchart TD
    Start([Start]) --> A[Student Login/Register]
    A --> B[Update Academic Profile + Documents]
    B --> C[Search Universities]
    C --> D[Open University Details]
    D --> E{Need to ask?}
    E -- No --> J{Apply now?}
    E -- Yes --> F[Start Chat Session]
    F --> G[Send Question]
    G --> H[System matches intent + FAQ]
    H --> I[Reply from DB data]
    I --> J
    J -- No --> C
    J -- Yes --> K[Submit Application]
    K --> L[Track Application Status]
    L --> End([End])
